      Type          CScript
      Name          "clamp trq_ref"
      Show          on
      Position      [2620, 505]
      Direction     up
      Flipped       off
      LabelPosition south
      CommentOut    DisabledOpenCircuit
      Parameter {
        Variable      "DialogGeometry"
